Markdown pages render through the same block parser as HTML, so
emphasis, strong text, inline code, strikethrough and absolute links all
carry through. Relative links resolve against the page URL: a nearby
post becomes absolute, and bare autolinks like
https://example.com/feed.xml work too.¹

